{{- define "custom.install.tldr" -}}
## TL;DR

```console
helm repo add {{ template "custom.repository.organization" . }} {{ template "custom.helm.url" . }}
helm repo update
helm install {{ template "chart.name" . }} {{ template "custom.helm.path" . }}
